msgctxt "#31290"
msgid "Thanks for using Aeon Tajo—I really hope you’re enjoying it. Creating and maintaining a Kodi skin like this takes hundreds of hours of work. If Aeon Tajo is something you enjoy and find useful, supporting it helps me keep working on it and ensures it can continue evolving in the future. [CR][CR]If you decide to do so, you’ll receive frequent updates with new features and bug fixes, along with videos, media packs, and easy-to-follow articles with detailed tips to help you get the most out of everything Aeon Tajo has to offer, together with my sincere gratitude for your support. [CR][CR]For more information, visit [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] and search for the creator [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], or go to [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Thanks!"
msgstr "Hvala vam što koristite Aeon Tajo — iskreno se nadam da vam se sviđa! Stvaranje i održavanje Kodi skina poput ovog zahteva stotine sati rada. Ako vam Aeon Tajo pruža zadovoljstvo i smatrate ga korisnim, vaša podrška mi pomaže da nastavim rad na njemu i osigurava da će se nastaviti razvijati u budućnosti. [CR][CR]Ako odlučite da to učinite, dobijate česta ažuriranja sa novim funkcijama i ispravkama grešaka, zajedno sa video zapisima, medijskim paketima i detaljnim člancima sa savetima za maksimalno iskorišćavanje svega što Aeon Tajo nudi, uz moju iskrenu zahvalnost za vašu podršku. [CR][CR]Za više informacija posetite [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] i potražite tvorca [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR] ili idite na [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Hvala!"

